{
  "ir_hash": "sha256:888cec16c1a12b96bbf4a7894653320063423c9ff2a2e371ceb5de464b6a7ffb",
  "knowledges": [
    {
      "content": "Bardeen-Cooper-Schrieffer (BCS) 理论将传统超导解释为声子交换介导的电子 Cooper 配对所产生的宏观量子态。该理论需要输入净有效电子-电子相互作用强度，即声子介导的吸引耦合与屏蔽 Coulomb 排斥之间的平衡。",
      "content_hash": "c77a71e08178bd8358a26230b62228884ba23bb9925f3761bcab5dcc74e466ee",
      "declaration_index": 0,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::bcs_framework",
      "label": "bcs_framework",
      "module": "motivation",
      "parameters": [],
      "type": "setting"
    },
    {
      "content": "Migdal-Eliashberg (ME) 框架通过在实频率轴上求解电子自能的自洽方程，将 BCS 理论推广到强耦合区间。然而，该框架将 Coulomb 赝势 $\\mu^*$ 作为唯象参数处理，通常通过拟合实验测量的超导转变温度 $T_c$ 来确定。对拟合参数的依赖限制了框架的预测能力，尤其是对于亚开尔文超导体，$\\mu^*$ 的微小变化会导致 $T_c$ 发生数量级变化。",
      "content_hash": "7da6bee9211a30643daa082ca933cebdff0b7dcc9bb8e78a3a1daa938a2aa19e",
      "declaration_index": 1,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::migdal_eliashberg",
      "label": "migdal_eliashberg",
      "module": "motivation",
      "parameters": [],
      "type": "setting"
    },
    {
      "content": "在传统金属中，Debye 频率 $\\omega_D$ 远小于 Fermi 能量 $E_F$（$\\omega_D / E_F \\ll 1$），建立了电子和声子能量尺度的分离。这一绝热条件由 Migdal（1958）首先利用，证明了电子-声子顶点修正是小量，从而允许向低能有效理论投影。",
      "content_hash": "4eeed089e30c874d1d88a2203cedf6fa615ffc13e162d60d925013a9fde5bf3e",
      "declaration_index": 2,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::adiabatic_approx",
      "label": "adiabatic_approx",
      "module": "motivation",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:migdal-1958",
          "version": "1958"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "均匀电子气（jellium 模型）在金属密度区间（Wigner-Seitz 半径 $r_s = 2$ 至 $6$）是简单金属理论的标准参考系统。其性质通过局域密度近似支撑了密度泛函理论，使其成为第一性原理多体方法的天然检验平台。",
      "content_hash": "f43f24fc696c4fdc8152674cdecb58fb8c9dcb7d3e552f136bd85d5729b98492",
      "declaration_index": 3,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::electron_gas_model",
      "label": "electron_gas_model",
      "module": "motivation",
      "parameters": [],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "Coulomb 赝势 $\\mu^*$——Migdal-Eliashberg 超导理论中的关键唯象参数——能否从第一性原理以可控精度计算？将第一性原理 $\\mu^*$ 值代入 Eliashberg 框架后，能否对简单金属的超导转变温度 $T_c$ 给出定量可靠的预测？",
      "content_hash": "fed5568282916d8529f5b95665ef4943dd3720707c5abdfdd517bcc07dcdd464",
      "declaration_index": 4,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::main_question",
      "label": "main_question",
      "module": "motivation",
      "parameters": [],
      "type": "question"
    },
    {
      "content": "电子-声子系统的总作用量可严格分解为 $S = S_e[\\bar{\\psi}, \\psi] + S_{ph}[u] + S_{e\\text{-}ph}[\\bar{\\psi}, \\psi, u] + S_{CT}[u]$，其中 $S_e$ 描述无近似的多电子相互作用，$S_{ph}$ 描述具有物理色散 $\\omega_{\\kappa q}$ 的声子，$S_{e\\text{-}ph}$ 通过密度-位移形式捕获电子-声子耦合，$S_{CT}$ 是反项，减去已包含在物理声子谱中的静态屏蔽。引入反项 $S_{CT}$ 确保微扰展开中声子传播子保持物理性质且不发生重复计数。",
      "content_hash": "bd9fbe29e0073ae91f3ade0762883b7e6592908659c38566b4790692f188ea07",
      "declaration_index": 0,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::electron_phonon_action",
      "label": "electron_phonon_action",
      "module": "s2_model",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "超导不稳定性通过反常顶点函数 $\\Lambda_{k\\omega}$ 满足的 Bethe-Salpeter 方程检测。BSE 积分核可严格分解为纯电子粒子-粒子相互作用 $\\tilde{\\Gamma}^e$ 与声子介导的吸引 $W^{ph}$ 两部分：$\\tilde{\\Gamma} = \\tilde{\\Gamma}^e + W^{ph} + O(\\omega_D / E_F)$，其中误差项由 Migdal 定理控制，在绝热极限下可忽略。此分解是后续将 Coulomb 和声子通道独立处理的理论基础。",
      "content_hash": "e75f9e0d4a63149b4ed9e44eb704fd1346dfa0845ead2cb83fc44b4839109070",
      "declaration_index": 1,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::bse_kernel_decomposition",
      "label": "bse_kernel_decomposition",
      "module": "s2_model",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "反常顶点函数在低频极限下遵循普适标度关系 $\\Lambda_0 = 1 / (1 + g \\ln(\\omega_\\Lambda / T)) + O(T)$，其中 $g$ 和 $\\omega_\\Lambda$ 是系统相关参数。对于 $g < 0$（净吸引），顶点在 $T_c = \\omega_\\Lambda \\exp(1/g)$ 处发散，标志 Cooper 不稳定性。通过在 $T_c$ 以上多个温度计算 $\\Lambda_0$ 并利用此对数标度律外推，可以避免在 $T_c$ 处进行计算困难的自洽求解而精确确定超导转变温度。该方法优于传统特征值追踪方法，因为后者在强排斥相互作用体系中缺乏可靠的外推方案。",
      "content_hash": "f326df4a44c77f4a82a758d5663255cd48a1949060fc57776237a65a9783cbde",
      "declaration_index": 2,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::precursory_cooper_flow",
      "label": "precursory_cooper_flow",
      "module": "s2_model",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "配对传播子可严格分解为相干（低能/IR）与非相干（高能/UV）分量：$G_{k,\\omega} G_{-k,-\\omega} = \\Pi_{BCS} + \\varphi_{k\\omega}$，其中相干部分 $\\Pi_{BCS} = (z^e)^2 / [(\\omega/z_\\omega^{ph})^2 + \\varepsilon_k^2] \\cdot \\Theta(\\omega_c - |\\varepsilon_k|)$，$z^e$ 为电子-电子相互作用的准粒子权重，$z_\\omega^{ph}$ 捕获电子-声子耦合的频率依赖重整化。此分解是将全 BSE 降到低能有效理论的数学基础。",
      "content_hash": "27ff23257483aacfe4369474acfce93da4a42c9a046c82f1047091a48d76250c",
      "declaration_index": 0,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::pair_propagator_decomposition",
      "label": "pair_propagator_decomposition",
      "module": "s3_downfolding",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在 downfolding 过程中，Coulomb 通道和声子通道之间的交叉耦合项（$\\tilde{\\Gamma}^e \\cdot \\varphi \\cdot W^{ph}$）被等离激元频率压制，量级为 $\\omega_c^2 / \\omega_p^2$。对于金属密度 $r_s \\geq 1$，$\\omega_c / \\omega_p \\lesssim 0.1$，故 $\\omega_c^2 / \\omega_p^2 \\lesssim 0.01$，保证了两个通道可独立处理。此压制依赖于动态屏蔽 Coulomb 相互作用在高频的渐近行为 $W^s \\propto (\\omega - \\omega')^2 / [(\\omega - \\omega')^2 + \\omega_p^2]$。",
      "content_hash": "1ac02b55e2f45bcaadd69406046cbb7e34958cbf12648385aa08eaab76d6352b",
      "declaration_index": 1,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::cross_term_suppressed",
      "label": "cross_term_suppressed",
      "module": "s3_downfolding",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "消去高能模式后，完整的 BSE 可严格降标为仅依赖频率的 Fermi 面方程：$\\Lambda_\\omega = \\eta_\\omega + \\pi T \\sum_{|\\omega'| < \\omega_c} (\\lambda_{\\omega\\omega'} - \\mu_{\\omega_c}) \\, z^{ph}_{\\omega'} / |\\omega'| \\, \\Lambda_{\\omega'}$，其中有效顶点可分离为 $\\tilde{\\Gamma}^{\\omega_c} = U^e + W^{ph} + O(\\omega_D/E_F, \\, \\omega_c^2/\\omega_p^2)$，$U^e$ 为纯电子贡献且不依赖声子细节。此结果的关键意义是：尽管微观 Coulomb 相互作用具有奇异的动量依赖性和复杂的动态屏蔽，投影后的有效电子-电子相互作用退化为频率无关的赝势 $\\mu_{\\omega_c}$。",
      "content_hash": "14142f52848f17b42296cf62ef5abfcae09bae2209e1cd0af1c2e49bb156d59e",
      "declaration_index": 2,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::downfolded_bse",
      "label": "downfolded_bse",
      "module": "s3_downfolding",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "Coulomb 赝势 $\\mu_{\\omega_c}$ 在能量尺度变换下满足 Bogoliubov-Tolmachev-Shirkov 关系：$\\mu_{\\omega_c} = \\mu_{\\omega_c'} / (1 + \\mu_{\\omega_c'} \\ln(\\omega_c'/\\omega_c))$。该关系确保物理可观测量不依赖于截断尺度的选择。在 Fermi 能量处定义的'裸'赝势 $\\mu_{E_F}$ 是物理上有意义且无重整化伪影的量。",
      "content_hash": "4a4c935270e8a7437b0298159f1a7a8b38a41ad10bcb276586fd143e9613fc44",
      "declaration_index": 3,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::pseudopotential_scale_relation",
      "label": "pseudopotential_scale_relation",
      "module": "s3_downfolding",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "利用变分图形蒙特卡洛方法计算均匀电子气在 $r_s \\in [1,6]$ 区间的 $\\mu_{E_F}$，结果为：$r_s=1$ 时 $\\mu_{E_F} = 0.28(1)$，$r_s=2$ 时 $0.53(2)$，$r_s=3$ 时 $0.77(5)$，$r_s=4$ 时 $1.0(2)$，$r_s=5$ 时 $1.3(2)$，$r_s=6$ 时 $1.8(8)$。这些值显著超出 Morel-Anderson 静态 RPA 估计值（在 $r_s=5$ 处约为三倍），差异来源于顶点修正和超越 RPA 的效应。",
      "content_hash": "3d156664cef9dc9d6bba7e676933e4f4c382dec820a7c01cd281357a33933957",
      "declaration_index": 4,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::mu_vdiagmc_values",
      "label": "mu_vdiagmc_values",
      "module": "s3_downfolding",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "动态 RPA 对 $r_s > 2$ 预测 $\\mu^*$ 为负值，意味着 Coulomb 相互作用在 Cooper 通道中变为净吸引。这一结果在物理上不合理，因为没有电子-声子耦合的纯电子系统不应出现传统超导。这表明 RPA 在这些密度下对赝势的计算已经失效。",
      "content_hash": "98a16266004539977bfc2359bd060bf3f9c37d8d459f753322c05f96c1440baa",
      "declaration_index": 5,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::rpa_predicts_negative_mu",
      "label": "rpa_predicts_negative_mu",
      "module": "s3_downfolding",
      "parameters": [],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "通过类铝参数（$r_s = 1.92$，$\\omega_D/E_F = 0.005$）的基准测试，比较完整频率-动量依赖的 BSE 解与简化的仅频率 downfolded BSE 解，两种方法得到的 $T_c$ 仅差 0.2%（$T_c^{full}/T_F = 10^{-5.668}$ vs $T_c^{approx}/T_F = 10^{-5.667}$），在 Debye 频率以下两者展现相同的普适对数标度行为。该基准验证了 downfolding 过程的定量精度。",
      "content_hash": "fb7159967eb20c07b9dcf9f85abcacd3336d106a2203a5ebf3f2ea2103e20e08",
      "declaration_index": 6,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::downfolding_validated",
      "label": "downfolding_validated",
      "module": "s3_downfolding",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "Downfolding 框架在三类体系中不可靠：（1）超致密体系（$r_s \\lesssim 0.01$，如白矮星内部），等离激元变软；（2）二维体系，无能隙等离激元模式使尺度分离条件在任何密度下都不成立；（3）强关联材料，强关联产生的软集体激发破坏了能量尺度层级。",
      "content_hash": "839e1a270a9452ed191087875ab96419de863cb51ae95a61d5d870ff687c5ff9",
      "declaration_index": 7,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::downfolding_limitations",
