      "module": "s4_pseudopotential",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "在有效场论（EFT）框架中，电子-电子相互作用对准粒子权重 $z^e$ 的修正、对屏蔽 Coulomb 相互作用 $v_q/\\varepsilon_q$ 的修正、以及对电子-声子顶点 $\\Gamma_3^e$ 的修正各自都很大，单独考虑时会显著偏离自由电子结果。",
      "content_hash": "f08693e1fa589b991b2dc73b0f3184e353fb12ae089209b40c32ed95bcf501d4",
      "declaration_index": 0,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::individual_corrections_large",
      "label": "individual_corrections_large",
      "module": "s5_eph_coupling",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "尽管各项修正单独很大，它们在有效电子-声子耦合中几乎精确抵消：$z^e \\cdot v_q/\\varepsilon_q \\cdot \\Gamma_3^e(k; q) \\approx v_q / [1 - (v_q + f_{xc}) \\cdot \\chi_0^e(q)]$，其中左侧是包含所有多体修正的 EFT 结果，右侧是基于线性响应理论的密度泛函微扰理论（DFPT）结果。图形化地说，电子-电子相互作用对准粒子权重 $z^e$ 的贡献被电子-声子顶点重整化 $\\Gamma_3^e$ 有效抵消。",
      "content_hash": "aed9a102240b310bc09f7f147587e3e4acc47499c6ddd8042987bb674e470367",
      "declaration_index": 1,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::corrections_cancel",
      "label": "corrections_cancel",
      "module": "s5_eph_coupling",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "通过变分图形蒙特卡洛方法在 $r_s \\in [1, 5]$ 区间的数值验证，EFT 与 DFPT 在 Fermi 面上所有相关动量传递（$|q| \\leq 2k_F$）范围内给出近乎完全一致的有效电子-声子耦合 $\\lambda$ 值。",
      "content_hash": "fbee050985695a4b25229e223a62f8c827be243a4e2deadb576679eb5c90bc8b",
      "declaration_index": 2,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::dfpt_validated_numerically",
      "label": "dfpt_validated_numerically",
      "module": "s5_eph_coupling",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "密度泛函微扰理论（DFPT）对简单金属的电子-声子耦合常数 $\\lambda$ 给出定量可靠的结果。这一结论由变分图形蒙特卡洛方法在 $r_s \\in [1,5]$ 区间的逐点基准测试确立：尽管准粒子权重 $z^e$、屏蔽和顶点修正各自偏离自由电子值很大，它们在有效耦合中几乎精确抵消，使得 DFPT 的线性响应结果与包含所有多体效应的有效场论结果一致。这意味着计算真实材料的 $T_c$ 时可直接使用现有的 DFPT 代码获取电子-声子耦合，而无需完整的多体计算。",
      "content_hash": "526a820fe81b32417f6daad2df8d2648d3fd22bcb99255476abe6643c6d73699",
      "declaration_index": 3,
      "exported": false,
      "id": "github:superconductivity_electron_liquids::dfpt_reliable_for_simple_metals",
      "label": "dfpt_reliable_for_simple_metals",
      "module": "s5_eph_coupling",
      "parameters": [],
      "provenance": [
        {
          "package_id": "paper:2512.19382",
          "version": "2024"
        }
      ],
      "type": "claim"
    },
    {
      "content": "Ward 恒等式和电子-声子顶点的规范不变性强制要求自能、屏蔽和顶点修正在长波极限下系统性地互相抵消。DFPT 中各项大修正的近精确抵消不是数值巧合，而是守恒律约束多体修正在物理可观测量中组合方式的必然结果。",
      "content_hash": "3e45977afe06f5e56469263da10b3fbc1dfef253cdb414dd014b5ea316b0bdf2",
      "declaration_index": 4,
      "exported": false,
